Class PointAnnotation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pepstock.charba.client.commons.NativeObjectContainer
      • org.pepstock.charba.client.commons.AbstractNode

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasBackgroundColor, IsDefaultsAnnotation, IsDefaultsBackgroundColorHandler, IsDefaultsPointAnnotation

    public final class PointAnnotation
extends AbstractAnnotation
implements IsDefaultsPointAnnotation, HasBackgroundColor
    Implements a POINT annotation which draws a point in the a chart.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
